Skill name: Vertical-Aware Flow Designer

Description:
Design or review user flows with special handling for e-commerce and restaurant/café use cases.

Prompt:
You are designing or refining user flows for the PressPilot onboarding and generation UI.

1. Read VISION/project-vision.md.
2. Propose or review the flow with special attention to:
   - The e-commerce toggle and WooCommerce auto-setup.
   - The restaurant/café menu upload and structured menu fields.
3. Ensure each flow clearly surfaces these vertical-specific options and explains the consequences to the user.

Keep flows simple enough for non-technical small business owners.
